f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後我發覺等人完全冇難度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a95285ea5ec1f7a263254e40eef8304ec2d31e85","tid":939594,"uid":73002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T19:31:59.000Z","msg":"屌埋佢老母<br />\n我以前條仔由一開始到散<br />\n準時次數一隻手數得曬<br />\n樓主3個鐘咪算少<br />\n我等咗佢5個鐘都試過"}]}